OL,3,CMinisters consider law ensuring
OL,4,Cparents of critically ill children get
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FUnder current law, parents of newborn
OL,8,Fbabies who become unwell within the
OL,9,Ffirst 28 days of life are entitled to
OL,10,Fpaid leave and job protection to be by
OL,11,Ftheir child's bedside.
OL,13,FBut if their child is diagnosed with
OL,14,Fcancer at 29 days old, the parents no
OL,15,Flonger have the right to financial
OL,16,Fsupport.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
