OL,7,F"Parents are being forced to sell
OL,8,Fhomes, clothes and chose whether they
OL,9,Fcan eat or feed their child," he said.
OL,11,FCeri and Frances were inspired to
OL,12,Fstart the charity It's Never You and
OL,13,Fcampaign for a law change in memory of
OL,14,Ftheir six-year-old son Hugh, who died
OL,15,Fof cancer in 2021.
OL,17,F"Those are the first words that
OL,18,FFrances said to me when he was
OL,19,Fdiagnosed back in 2020: 'You always
OL,20,Fthink it's someone else. It's never
OL,21,Fyou'," Ceri said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
