OL,7,F"After he passed away, and during the
OL,8,Ftime that he had treatment, we
OL,9,Fwitnessed parents just going through
OL,10,Fthe worst time, obviously looking
OL,11,Fafter their child, but also the worst
OL,12,Ftime financially.
OL,14,F"And we realised at that point there
OL,15,Fis nothing in place in the UK that
OL,16,Fprovides support, financial support to
OL,17,Fparents of a sick child."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
