OL,7,FThey are hoping to amend the
OL,8,FEmployment Rights Bill, which is
OL,9,Fmaking its way through Parliament, to
OL,10,Fenshrine a new right to statutory paid
OL,11,Fleave and job protection from day one
OL,12,Ffor parents whose child is diagnosed
OL,13,Fwith a critical or terminal illness,
OL,14,Fup to the age of 16.
OL,16,FMany workplaces will provide support
OL,17,Fto their staff but there is nothing in
OL,18,Flaw forcing them to.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
