OL,7,F"This is about basic equality," said
OL,8,FFrances. "All Parents of sick children
OL,9,Fface emotional devastation and
OL,10,Ffinancial stress and yet there is no
OL,11,Fguaranteed support. Help should not be
OL,12,Fcut off when a child turns 29 days
OL,13,Fold, the stress, the anxiety and the
OL,14,Fworries are still all the same."
OL,16,FWatch: Frances and Ceri speak to ITV
OL,17,FNews outside Downing Street
OL,19,FTheir local MP, Chris Hinchliff of the
OL,20,FLabour Party, urged Prime Minister
OL,21,FKeir Starmer to listen to the couple.
