OL,7,FAt present, parents of critically ill
OL,8,Fchildren must rely on unpaid Carer's
OL,9,FLeave, which is capped at just one
OL,10,Fweek per year. Disability living
OL,11,Fallowance is available to claim on
OL,12,Fbehalf of the child, but parents must
OL,13,Fwait 90 days before applying and an
OL,14,Fapplication can take up to 20 weeks to
OL,15,Fbe processed.
